#

Asian-Infused Salmon Delight

$25.5
680 kcal
Difficulty: 60%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

fishsoy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteingluten-free

Tags:

dinnerseafoodasian-inspired

Description

A beautifully glazed salmon with rich soy and ginger notes, accompanied by tender asparagus and aromatic saffron rice.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 4 pieces
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • fresh ginger, grated: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • honey: 2 tablespoons
  • sesame oil: 1 tablespoon
  • asparagus: 1 pound
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • basmati rice: 1 cup
  • saffron threads: 1/2 teaspoon
  • chicken or vegetable broth: 2 cups
  • lemon zest: 1 teaspoon
  • green onions, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • toasted sesame seeds: 1 tablespoon
